        // The key property: when left was at position a and right was at position r,
        // we had that s[r] was in {s[a], ..., s[r-1]}. So s[a..r+1) is NOT unique.
        // Since s[a..r) WAS unique, the maximal unique substring starting at a has length exactly r-a.
